data.description: Exquisite both inside and out! Nestled in the meticulously maintained El Rio Country Club Golf Course community, this immaculate home graces the beautiful green of the golf course, providing breathtaking, unobstructed views. As you enter the property you will be welcomed by exquisite landscaping and beautiful cool decking entry way. Boasting 3 garage spaces, boat deep with a mini split AC unit, an inviting entry, and a spacious open split-bedroom floor plan with vaulted ceilings, this pride of ownership home features attractive wood plank tile flooring throughout the main living and carpet in the bedrooms. New energy efficient cellular shades through out the house for optimal temperature control and privacy. The kitchen, a culinary delight, showcases a granite bar top, stainless steel appliances including an electric smooth-top stove, built-in microwave, fridge, dishwasher, and a generously sized pantry. The residence comprises 3 bedrooms and a den, and 2 bathrooms, with the main suite offering a walk-in closet, dual sink vanity, and a walk-in shower. Savor breathtaking sunsets from the comfort of your full-length back patio, impeccably adorned with the cooling decking. This beautifully finished outdoor space invites you to unwind in style, providing a perfect backdrop for relaxation Embrace the lifestyle of this golf course community, conveniently located near the Colorado River, Lake Mohave, and the vibrant attractions of Laughlin. Don't miss the chance to experience this exceptional home.
